Saurin karuwar cutar COVID-19 a cikin EU/EEA da UK, 1 ga Janairu zuwa 15 ga Maris, 2020
Tsarin da ya yi daidai da karuwar adadin masu kamuwa da cutar COVID-19 a cikin EU/EEA da Burtaniya ya tabbatar da cewa, duk da cewa matakan sun bambanta a kowace ƙasa, yaduwar COVID-19 ta karu cikin sauri a cikin dukkan ƙasashe.
Kamar yadda aka nuna a cikin kwarewar Italiya, ƙasashe, asibitoci da kuma ɗakunan kulawa mai tsanani suna buƙatar haɓaka kasancewa don fuskantar karuwar masu cutar COVID-19 waɗanda ke buƙatar kulawa ta musamman da kulawa ta musamman.
A ranar 31 ga Disamba, 2019, an ba da rahoton wasu mutane da suka kamu da cutar SIDS da ba a san dalilin da ya haifar da ita ba a Wuhan, lardin Hubei na kasar Sin.
A ranar 9 ga Janairu, 2020, Cibiyar Kula da Cututtuka da Cututtuka ta Sin ta bayyana cewa cutar ta samo asali ne daga sabon kwayar cutar da ake kira coronavirus 2 respiratory respiratory syndrome coronavirus 2-SARS-CoV.
Tun daga wannan lokacin, ana kiran cutar mai saurin kamuwa da cutar 2-SARS-CoV da cutar COVID-19.
Shaida ya nuna cewa har zuwa yau kashi 80% na masu cutar COVID-19 suna da rauni, watau, kamuwa da cutar huhu ba tare da cutar huhu ba ko tare da cutar huhu kuma yawancin suna warkewa.
14% na masu cutar COVID-19 sun buƙaci asibiti, kuma sauran 6% na marasa lafiya sun buƙaci kulawa mai mahimmanci.
Yawan mutuwar mutanen da suka kamu da cutar COVID-19 ya kai kusan kashi 4 cikin dari.
A cikin wannan binciken, mun bincika yanayin yanayin COVID-19 a cikin kowace EU / EEA da Burtaniya, da kuma kwatanta su da yanayin lardin Hubei na China.
Hakanan muna kwatanta adadin COVID-19 na yanzu a cikin ƙasashen EU/EEA da Burtaniya tare da adadin masu cutar a Italiya daga 31 ga Janairu-15 ga Maris, 2020.
COVID-19 a cikin EU / EEA da Burtaniya
Bayan China, COVID-19 ya bazu a wurare da yawa kuma ya haifar da irin wannan yanayin a sauran ƙasashe.
A ranar 11 ga Maris, 2020, Babban Daraktan Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya (WHO) ya ayyana COVID-19 a matsayin annobar duniya.
A ranar 5 ga Maris, Spiteri da abokan aikinsa sun ba da sanarwar cutar COVID-19 ta farko da aka tabbatar a Turai, a cewar Eurosurveillance 2020.
A cikin ƙasashen EU/EAA, an ba da rahoton farkon kamuwa da cutar guda uku a ranar 24 ga Janairu 2020 tsakanin mutanen da suka dawo daga Wuhan, lardin Hubei na China.
A ranar 15 ga Maris, 2020, an sami karuwar COVID-19 a cikin dukkan ƙasashe 30 na EU/EAA da Burtaniya, wanda ya haifar da rahoton mutane 39,768 da suka kamu da cutar a tsakanin 31 ga Disamba, 2019 zuwa wannan shekarar, ciki har da mutuwar 1,727, wanda ya haɗa da kamuwa da cutar 17,750 da mutuwar 1,441 a Italiya.
Samun ƙididdigar ƙididdiga da ƙididdigar ƙididdigar COVID-19
A cikin Cibiyar Kula da Cututtuka ta Turai (ECDC), ana samun adadin rahoton COVID-19 a kowace ƙasa daga tushe na hukuma kamar ma'aikatun kiwon lafiya na ƙasa, hukumomin kiwon lafiya na yanki da WHO, kuma ana sabunta su kowace rana da karfe 8:00 na safe.
An yi amfani da wannan bayanan don tantance yanayin COVID-19 a cikin EU da Burtaniya da kuma kwatanta su da Italiya.
A matsayin mai kula da ci gaban COVID-19 mai aiki, mun lissafa jimlar jimlar kwanaki 14 na COVID-19 kuma mun yi la'akari da yanayin yanayin COVID-19 a kowace EU da UK a cikin Janairu-1 Maris 15, 2020.
Mun kuma gabatar da adadin wadanda aka ba da rahoton cutar a kowace ƙasa a karfe 8:00 na safiyar 15 ga Maris idan aka kwatanta da adadin a Italiya a ranar 31 ga Janairu zuwa 15 ga Maris.
Hanyar COVID-19 a cikin EU da Birtaniya
Jerin gajeren kwana 14 na rikodin COVID-19 a cikin EU da Burtaniya gabaɗaya suna bin tsarin lardin lardin Hubei na China (Figure 1.
A cikin EU da Burtaniya, adadin masu kamuwa da COVID-19 ya fara ƙaruwa a ranar 21 ga Fabrairu, kuma ya ƙaru sosai a ranar 28 ga Fabrairu, 2020 (wanda ya nuna cewa ba a yi ba).
Wannan ya faru ne saboda karuwar yawan masu kamuwa da cutar a Italiya, amma duk sauran ƙasashen EU da Burtaniya sun nuna irin wannan karuwar a cikin adadin masu kamuwa da COVID-19 a cikin ƙasashensu.
Shafi na 2 ya nuna karuwar adadin masu cutar COVID-19 a cikin Tarayyar Turai da Burtaniya da Italiya tsakanin 31 ga Janairu zuwa 15 ga Maris, 2020.
Wannan yana nuna cewa a ranar 15 ga Maris da karfe 8:00 na safe, adadin mutanen da suka kamu a cikin wasu ƙasashen EU 15 da Burtaniya sun yi daidai da adadin mutanen da suka kamu a Italiya a cikin makonni uku ko ƙasa da haka a cikin wannan makon.
Sakamakon bincikenmu ya nuna cewa adadin wadanda suka kamu da cutar COVID-19 a kasashen EU da Birtaniya na karuwa cikin sauri.
Abubuwan da ake gani na ƙaruwar COVID-19 ya nuna cewa cutar ta yadu da sauri a cikin ƙasashe daban-daban.
Wannan ya faru ne duk da cewa ƙasashe suna cikin matakai daban-daban kuma ba su da daidaito a cikin matakan lafiyar jama'a na ƙasa, da kuma bambance-bambance a cikin ma'anar yanayi da kuma hanyoyin da ake amfani da su don gano marasa lafiya don gwaji don tabbatar da cutar COVID-19.
A farkon watan Maris na 2020, likitocin da ke yankin da aka kamu da cutar a Italiya sun bayyana cewa kusan kashi 10 cikin 100 na masu kamuwa da cutar COVID-19 na buƙatar kulawa mai tsanani, kuma kafofin watsa labarai sun ba da rahoton cewa asibitoci da rukunin kulawa da gaggawa a waɗannan yankuna sun kai iyakar ƙarfin su.
Bayanai na asibiti da na ICU na marasa lafiya da ke fama da COVID-19 a cikin EU/EEA sun kai kashi 6 cikin ɗari da 1 cikin ɗari na masu cutar a halin yanzu (ba a nuna bayanan ba).
Koyaya, dole ne a tattara waɗannan bayanan a cikin tsari mai kyau don kammala bayanan kulawa na yanzu wanda ke mai da hankali kan yawan shari'o'in da aka ruwaito da yawan mace-mace.
Wani bincike da aka gudanar a watan Nuwamba 2010 ya nuna bambancin da ke tsakanin adadin gadaje a cikin kulawar marasa lafiya da kuma cibiyoyin kulawa na likita a Turai, inda a Jamus adadin ya kai gadaje 29.2 da kuma a Portugal gadaje 4.2 ga kowane mutum 100,000.
Wannan yana nuna cewa ƙasashe na iya samun ƙasa ko sama da albarkatu fiye da Italiya (12.5 ICU gadoji a kowace 100,000 a cikin Nuwamba 2020).
Halin da ake ciki na yanayin da aka danganta da yawan ƙarfin kulawa da lafiya, tare da ƙididdigar cutar a cikin EU da Burtaniya game da yaduwar COVID-19 na rashin lafiya da ke da alaƙa da haɗarin fiye da 90% na ƙarfin ƙarfin kulawa da lafiya, an bayyana a cikin sabon sabuntawa na shida na ECDC Rapid COVID-19 Risk Assessment.
Saboda yawan adadin masu kamuwa da cutar a cikin EU da Birtaniya, da kuma asibitoci da dakunan kula da marasa lafiya da ke kula da mutanen da ke cikin wani yanki, ya fi dacewa a tattara bayanai kan yawan masu kamuwa da cutar da kuma yawan marasa lafiya a cikin rukunin ƙididdigar yanki na matakin 2 (2-NUTS).
Kwarewar Italiya da yanayin da ake ciki a wasu ƙasashe sun nuna cewa COVID-19 yana yaduwa cikin sauri a cikin EU da Burtaniya.
Kasashe, asibitoci da kuma sassan kula da masu cutar masu tsanani dole ne su shirya don yanayin da zai iya haifar da ci gaba da yaduwar SARS-CoV-2 a cikin al'umma da kuma karuwar masu cutar COVID-19 da ke buƙatar kulawa ta kiwon lafiya da kulawa ta musamman, kamar yadda ake gani a yanzu a yankunan da ke fama da cutar a Italiya.
A cewar sabon binciken ECDC na gaggawa, ana buƙatar hanzarta aiwatar da tsari mai mahimmanci don rage yaduwar cutar coronavirus 2-SARS-COV, tare da sauya tsarin daga riƙewa zuwa ragewa, saboda yawan saurin da ake tsammani na ƙididdigar lamura ba zai kasance da cikakken lokaci ga masu yanke shawara da asibitoci ba don fahimta, daidaitawa da daidaitawa idan ya cancanta kuma ba a kan lokaci ba.
Binciken haɗarin gaggawa ya kuma tsara matakan kiwon lafiyar jama'a don rage tasirin wannan annobar ta duniya.
Yanzu akwai wata dama ta musamman da ƙasashe za su iya ƙarawa don rage yaduwar cutar SARS-CoV-2 da rage matsin lamba kan kula da lafiya.
Idan hakan bai yi nasara ba, tsarin kiwon lafiya na sauran ƙasashen EU zai iya shiga cikin kwanaki ko makonni masu zuwa tare da yawan waɗanda ke buƙatar kulawa mai tsanani.
Cutar COVID-19, wanda ya haifar da cutar coronavirus 2 (2-SARS-CoV) ta haifar da cutar cututtukan huhu mai saurin kamuwa da cuta (SARS) ya kashe mutane sama da 3,000 kuma ya kamu da cutar fiye da 80,000 a China da sauran ƙasashe na duniya, wanda zai iya haifar da bala'i ga mutane.
Kamar kwayar cutar SARS-CoV, wanda ya kamu da dubban mutane a 2003, sabon kwayar cutar SARS-CoV-2 na iya zama mai saurin kamuwa da cutar a cikin ƙuda kuma yana haifar da alamun bayyanar cututtuka ta hanyar irin wannan tsari.
COVID-19 ba shi da haɗari da mutuwa fiye da SARS, amma yana da yawan watsawa kuma yana shafar tsofaffi da maza fiye da matasa da mata.
Wannan labarin ya fito ne saboda karuwar adadin cututtukan da ke da alaƙa da wannan sabuwar cuta, yana ba da cikakken bayani game da saurin ci gaban bincike.
Za mu tattauna muhimman al'amuran ilimin cututtuka, ilimin cututtuka, ilimin ƙwayoyin cuta, ganewar asali, magani, da kuma rigakafin cutar.
Duk da cewa har yanzu akwai tambayoyi da yawa da za a yi, muna fatan wannan binciken zai taimaka wajen fahimtar da kuma hana wannan mummunar cuta.
Bikin bazara na ranar 25 ga Janairu, 2020 ya zama abin tunawa ga jama'ar kasar Sin saboda an tilasta musu yin hutun hutunsu na tsawon makonni a gida bayan barkewar cutar.
Wannan kwayar cutar tana da kamanceceniya da kwayar cutar coronavirus (CoV) wacce ta haifar da cutar sankara mai saurin kamuwa da cutar sankara (SARS) a shekarar 2003; saboda haka Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya (WHO) ta ba da sunan SARS-CoV-2 a ranar 11 ga Fabrairu 2020 da kuma cutar da ke haifar da ita COVID-19.
An gano cewa cutar ta fara ne a Wuhan, China, kuma ta yadu cikin sauri a duk faɗin ƙasar da kuma kusan ƙasashe 50 na duniya.
A ranar 2 ga Maris, 2020, cutar ta kai adadin mutane 80,000 da aka tabbatar sun kamu da cutar COVID-19, wanda ya kai 40,000 da suka warke, tare da mutuwar mutane fiye da 3,000.
WHO ta yi gargadin cewa COVID-19 shine "maƙiyi na farko na jama'a" kuma ya fi ta'addanci ƙarfi.
A cikin ƙasa da watanni biyu, an buga labarai sama da 200 game da COVID-19, wanda ya shafi ilimin ƙwayoyin cuta, ilimin halittu, ilimin halayya, ganewar asali da magani, tun bayan da aka ba da rahoton cutar ta farko a ranar 7 ga Janairu, 2020, kuma an gano jerin kwayoyin halittar kwayar cutar a cikin marasa lafiya da yawa, in ji PubMed.
Wannan bita na kokarin tattara yanayin bincike a cikin wannan sabon binciken da ake yi a cikin sauri.
Da zarar ya fara, muna ƙoƙarin kwatanta COVID-19 da SARS da sauran cututtukan coronavirus da cutar ta gabas ta tsakiya ta numfashi (MERS, 2012 pandemic).
Muna kuma tattauna abin da muka sani game da rigakafin cutar da kuma abin da za ta iya haifar da shi, da kuma wasu tambayoyi masu muhimmanci da ba a amsa ba.
Coronaviruses ana ɗaukarsu a matsayin masu cutarwa ga mutane kuma suna da alhakin kusan kashi 15% na mura na yau da kullun.
Duk da haka, a cikin wannan karni, mun fuskanci mutum-mai-mutu coronavirus sau biyu, SARS-CoV da MERS-CoV, wanda ya haifar da barkewar cutar a China a 2003 da Saudi Arabia a 2012, kuma da sauri ya bazu a cikin ƙasashe da yawa a duniya, yana haifar da mummunan kamuwa da cuta da mutuwa.
Wannan na nufin cewa COVID-19 ita ce cutar koronaviral ta uku da ta fi yawa a tarihin ɗan adam.
Hakanan an nuna a cikin adadi na 1.1.1, an fara samun kamuwa da cutar ta hanta da ba a san asalin ta ba a Wuhan a ranar 31 ga Disamba, 2019 a Hukumar Lafiya ta kasar Sin.
Bayan mako guda, an fitar da jerin kwayoyin halittar kwayar cutar corona.
A ranar 15 ga Janairu, 2020, an ba da rahoton mutuwar farko a Wuhan.
A wannan lokacin, cutar ta yadu cikin sauri a birane, larduna da kuma kasashe masu makwabtaka da su.
A ranar 20 ga Janairu, an ba da sanarwar kamuwa da cutar a tsakanin ma'aikatan kiwon lafiya, kuma an ba da sanarwar cewa cutar na iya yaduwa daga mutum zuwa mutum.
A ranar 23 ga Janairu, an kebe Wuhan kuma an dakatar da dukkan sassan sufuri.
A ranar 24 ga Disamba, wani bincike na farko ya nuna cewa daga cikin mutane 41 da aka tabbatar sun kamu da cutar, 21 ne kawai suka kamu da cutar daga kasuwannin abincin teku, wanda hakan ya sa aka gano asalin cutar daga wani dabbobin da ba a san asalinsa ba.
A ranar 30 ga Janairu, Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya ta ayyana barkewar cutar a matsayin matsalar gaggawa ta duniya.
Ya zuwa lokacin wannan rahoton, cutar ta bazu a duk faɗin China da kusan ƙasashe 50 a duniya.
Saboda yanayin yana tasowa da sauri, tsawon lokaci da kuma tsananin cutar ta kasance a buɗe.
A ranar 11 ga Fabrairu, 2020, an gudanar da bincike mai zurfi a kan marasa lafiya 8,866 wanda ya nuna cewa 4,021 sun kamu da cutar COVID-19 wanda ya nuna sabon hoto na cutar a cikin al'umma (https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/UlBi-HX_rHPXa1qHA2bhdA).
SARS-CoV-2 yana shafar mutane a cikin kowane zamani, amma mafi yawan mutane suna tsakanin shekaru 30-65.
Kusan rabin (47.7%) na masu kamuwa da cutar sun kasance sama da shekaru 50, kaɗan ne daga cikinsu suna ƙasa da shekaru 20, kuma 14 ne kawai ke ƙasa da shekaru 10.
Matsakaicin kamuwa da cutar SARS-CoV-2 ya kasance mafi girma a cikin maza (0.31/100,000) fiye da mata (0.27/100,000).
An samu karuwar masu cutar COVID-19 a Hubei da kewayenta.
COVID-19 yakan ɗauki matsakaicin kwanaki 5 (9-2) kafin a iya gano mutum.
A matsakaici, tsawon lokaci daga kamuwa zuwa bayyanar cutar shine kwanaki 4.8 (7.2-3.0).
Hakanan yana kashe mutum a cikin matsakaicin kwanaki 9.5 (13-4.8).
Matsakaicin farfadowa na farko (R0) na cutar shine 3.77 (95% CI:3.51-4.05), kuma daidaitaccen farfadowa na R0 shine 4.82-2.32.
Adadin masu kamuwa da cutar ya karu sosai kafin 23 ga Disamba, wanda ya zo daidai da yawan zirga-zirga da kuma jigilar mutane kafin bikin bazara na China.
Halin mutuwa a cikin tabbatattun lamura ya kai 1.44% (95% CI:1.10-1.86%) kuma daidaitaccen mutuwar a cikin dukkan masu kamuwa da cutar ya kai 3.06% (95% CI:2.02-4.59%).
Abubuwa uku da suka fi haifar da haɗarin kamuwa da COVID-19 sune jinsi (maza), shekaru (sama da 60), da cututtukan numfashi.
Coronaviruses suna cikin manyan, masu kama da juna, waɗanda ke ƙunshe da RNA.
Ana iya rarraba shi zuwa nau'i huɗu, wato, Alpha, Beta, Gamma, da Delta. Guda biyu na Alpha da Beta coronaviruses suna iya cutar da mutane.
A cikin SARS-CoV da MERS-CoV, kwayar glycoprotein spike (S) tana haɗuwa da enzyme mai canza angiotensin 2 (ACE2) da mai karɓar dipeptidyl peptidase 4 (DPP4) tare da haɗuwa da ƙwayar cuta.
