Ana buƙatar sabunta sigogin gano cutar COVID-19 "abin da ake zargi" da "abin da aka tabbatar".
A ranar 6 ga Fabrairu, 2020, ƙungiyarmu ta ba da umarnin gaggawa don ganowa da magance cutar Coronavirus 2019 (2019-nCoV), wannan jagorar ta ba da damar kwarewarmu da kuma ba da shawara ga masu fama da cutar a duniya.
Koyaya, cutar Coronavirus ta 2019 (COVID-19) sabon cuta ne, wanda ke ci gaba da haɓaka ƙwarewarmu da iliminmu dangane da ci gaba da binciken bincike da ƙwarewar aikin asibiti; saboda haka, ana ci gaba da sabunta hanyoyin ganowa da hanyoyin magani.
A cikin wannan labarin, mun amsa wata tambaya game da jagororinmu kuma mun gabatar da sabon ƙirar ganewar asali don "ainihin hali" da "ainihin hali" bisa ga sabon jagorar ganewar asali da magani don COVID-19 (bugu na bakwai) wanda Kwamitin Lafiya na Kasa na Jamhuriyar Jama'ar Sin ya wallafa.
A watan Disamba na 2019, sabon coronavirus na 2019 (2019-nCoV) ya fara yaduwa, wanda yanzu ake kira da sunan cutar coronavirus 2019 (COVID-2019) kuma an kira cutar da sunan SARS-CoV-2 (SARS-CoV-2).
A ranar 11 ga Maris, 2020, Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya ta ayyana COVID-19 a matsayin annoba ta duniya.
Don yaƙi da cutar SARS-CoV-2, ƙungiyarmu ta haɓaka jagorar shawarwari na gaggawa wanda aka buga akan layi a cikin Nazarin Likita na Soja a ranar 6 ga Fabrairu, 2020.
Tun lokacin da aka buga shi, ya jawo hankali sosai.
lura: Kodayake COVID-19 sabon cuta ne, iliminmu yana ƙaruwa bisa ga ci gaba da binciken bincike da ƙwarewar aikin asibiti; saboda haka, ana sabunta hanyoyin bincike da magani.
Misali, umarnin ganowa da magani don COVID-19 wanda Kwamitin Lafiya na Kasa na Jamhuriyar Jama'ar Sin ya wallafa (http://www.nhc.gov.cn/), ya buga jimlar lambobi bakwai tsakanin 16 ga Janairu, 2020 zuwa 3 ga Maris, 2020, tare da wasu abubuwan da suka canza sosai.
Yanzu, a cikin wannan jagorar, mun sami wani bayani daga Zhou et al. wanda ya ba da shawarar yin amfani da ƙididdigar ƙididdiga mai sauƙi daga gwajin asibiti.
Ayyukan su sun ba da sabon tabbaci ga umarninmu kuma sun ba da babbar alama ga wannan annoba ta duniya.
Muna goyon bayan su kuma muna godiya da su saboda wannan gagarumin aiki.
Koyaya, aikin su yana buƙatar sabuntawa tare da sabbin hanyoyin bincike da magani na COVID-19 (sashi na gwaji na 7) da kuma sababbin bincike.
Dangane da fitowar ta bakwai (Maris 3, 2020), don tabbatar da cewa ana tsammanin akwai buƙatar haɗa kowane ɗayan abubuwan da ke cikin tarihin cutar tare da abubuwa biyu na alamar asibiti don yin cikakken bincike, ko kuma dole ne a haɗa abubuwa uku na asibiti idan tarihin cutar ba shi da kyau:
Tarihin cututtukan: (1) Tarihin tafiya ko zama a Wuhan da kewayen birni, ko kuma sauran al'ummomi inda aka ba da rahoton cutar COVID-19 a cikin kwanaki 14 da suka gabata kafin bayyanar cututtuka; (2) Tarihin saduwa da wanda ya kamu da cutar SARS-CoV-2 (tare da gwajin kwayar nucleic acid mai kyau); (3) Tarihin saduwa da marasa lafiya da ke da alamomin cutar ta numfashi a Wuhan da kewayen birni, ko kuma sauran al'ummomi inda aka ba da rahoton cutar ta COVID-19 a cikin kwanaki 14 da suka gabata kafin bayyanar cututtuka; (4) Tarihin saduwa da tarin lamuran da aka tabbatar (>= 2 lamuran da ke da alamomin cutar ta numfashi da suka faru a cikin makonni 2 a cikin ƙananan wurare, kamar gidaje, ofisoshi, makarantu, da sauransu).
Alamar asibiti: (1) alamun rashin lafiya na numfashi da/ko; (2) tare da alamun COVID-19 na cutar ta radiation; (3) ƙarancin adadin ƙwayoyin farin jini wanda ke nuna ƙimar al'ada, ƙarancin, ko kuma raguwar ƙwayoyin lymphocyte a farkon matakin.
Ya kamata a tantance tabbataccen yanayin bisa ga yanayin da ake zargi da cutar ko kuma hujjojin siru: (1) gwajin lokaci na PCR na SARS-CoV-2 mai kyau; (2) cikakken kwayar halittar kwayar halitta wanda ke nuna asalin asalin kwayar cutar coronavirus; (3) tabbatacce ga IgM antigen da IgG antigen na SARS-CoV-2 a cikin gwajin kwayar; ko canji a cikin IgG antigen na SARS-CoV-2 daga mara kyau zuwa tabbatacce, ko kuma =>4 sau da yawa a cikin lokacin dawowa bayan cutar ta tashi.
Za mu iya ganin cewa an ƙara gwajin PCR na ainihi don nucleic acid a cikin hanyoyin numfashi ko samfurin jini zuwa na biyu (Janairu 18, 2020) da na uku (Janairu 22, 2020).
An ƙara gano cututtukan cututtuka a cikin samfurin jini a cikin juzu'i na huɗu (Janairu 27, 2020) da juzu'i na biyar (Fabrairu 8, 2020); sannan kuma an ƙara hujja ta serological a cikin juzu'i na bakwai.
Waɗannan gyare-gyare sun dogara ne akan ci gaba da aikin masu bincike na neman kayan gano nucleic acid don saurin ganewa, tare da samfurin numfashi wanda ya haɗa da samfurin jini, wanda ya inganta wadatar samfurori daban-daban, kuma ya ba da damar samar da sakamako mai kyau na maganin rigakafi na musamman a cikin iyakokin da aka tabbatar.
Duk da haka, akwai ƙarin tabbaci da ke nuna cewa ya kamata mu mai da hankali ga cututtukan cututtuka da cututtuka marasa cututtuka.
Saboda haka, dole ne a sabunta jadawalin Zhou et al., saboda sun yi la'akari da mutumin da ba shi da alamun cutar a matsayin "mai ƙarancin haɗari".
Hakanan ana buƙatar yin amfani da tsarin kulawa don ƙarin bincike da aikin asibiti.
A sakamakon haka, muna fatan za a sami ƙarin shaidu kai tsaye kuma muna roƙon masu karatu su ba da ra'ayoyinsu.
Don gano "al'amuran da ake zargi" da "al'amuran da aka tabbatar", muna ba da shawarar bin diddigin da kuma bin ƙa'idodin da aka sabunta don ƙasashen su.
Ƙungiyarmu za ta sabunta jagororinmu na bayar da taimako a lokaci-lokaci.
Bangladesh ta ba da rahoton sabbin mutuwar COVID-19 guda biyar, mafi yawan adadin yau da kullun
A ranar Litinin, Bangladesh ta tabbatar da mutuwar mutum biyar daga COVID-19 a ranar.
Wannan shi ne adadi mafi yawa na mutuwar da aka samu a cikin rana guda sakamakon cutar.
A jiya, Hukumar Kula da Cututtuka da Cututtuka ta Bangladesh (IEDCR) ta ba da rahoton adadin masu kamuwa da cutar, wanda ya haɗa da 114 masu aiki da 33 da suka warke a gida.
An yi rahoton mutuwar mutane 17.
A cikin wani bayani na kokarin da aka yi a kan layi, mai kula da IEDCR, Mista Mirjai Sabrina Flora, ya ce mutuwar ta kasance maza hudu da mace daya.
