A ranar Asabar, a cikin sanarwar bidiyo ta kan layi, Ministan Wayoyi da Bridges, Ubaidul Qader ya ce za a dakatar da zirga-zirgar jama'a na tsawon lokaci fiye da yadda aka tsara, har zuwa wannan maraice.
An fara dakatar da zirga-zirgar jama'a a ranar 26 ga Maris, kuma an shirya za a ƙare a ranar Asabar, 4 ga Afrilu.
