An fara samun mutum biyu da suka kamu da COVID-19 a Bangladesh a ranar 8 ga Maris, biyu daga cikinsu sun dawo daga Italiya tare da matar ɗaya daga cikinsu.
A ranar 19 ga Maris, an dawo da su uku.
SARS-CoV-2 ya wuce miliyan daya a duniya
A ranar Alhamis, jimlar adadin wadanda suka kamu da cutar coronavirus SARS-CoV-2 a duniya ya zarce miliyan daya, a cewar bayanan Jami'ar Johns Hopkins.
Akalla mutane dubu 52 ne suka mutu sanadiyyar COVID-19, cutar da ke haifar da kwayar cutar corona.
Wannan babban canji ya faru ne a ranar da Malawi ta ba da sanarwar farkon kamuwa da cutar coronavirus da Zambia ta ba da sanarwar mutuwar farko da ke da alaƙa da cutar.
A ranar Alhamis, Koriya ta Arewa ta ba da sanarwar cewa tana ɗaya daga cikin ƙananan ƙasashe da ba su da cutar coronavirus.
Har zuwa jiya, Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya ta ba da rahoton 1,051,635 da aka tabbatar da cutar, ciki har da 79,332 a cikin awanni ashirin da huɗu kafin karfe 10 na safe agogon Turai ta Tsakiya (0800 UTC) a ranar 4 ga Afrilu.
A Amurka, an sami fiye da 244,000 da suka kamu da cutar coronavirus, tare da aƙalla mutuwar 5,900.
