Majalisar dokokin Portugal ta kada kuri'a don tsawaita dokar ta baci ta ƙasa har zuwa kwanaki 15; kuri'ar ta amince da kuri'u 215, saɓani 10, da ƙuri'a ɗaya.
Saudi Arabia ta kara tsawaita dokar hana zirga-zirga a cikin biranen Makkah da Madina har zuwa ranar; a baya, dokar hana zirga-zirga ta kasance daga 3 na yamma zuwa 6 na safe.
