A ranar Juma'a da yammacin Juma'a, manyan kantin sayar da kayayyaki na Woolworths da Coles na Australiya sun rage iyakokin sayan kayan wanka na Clinkx zuwa fakiti biyu da fakiti ɗaya a kowane ma'amala a duk shagunan da ke cikin ƙasa.
