Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya ta ayyana COVID-19 a matsayin annoba ta duniya
A ranar Laraba, Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya (WHO) ta ayyana ci gaba da yaduwar COVID-19 - cutar da ke haifar da kwayar cutar coronavirus SARS-CoV-2 - a matsayin annoba ta duniya.
Kodayake kalmar "annoba" tana nuna yadda cutar ta yadu, ba yadda wasu cututtuka ke da haɗari ba, WHO ta yi nuni da cewa gwamnatoci na buƙatar ɗaukar mataki:
Babban Daraktan Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya, Dr. Tedros Adhanom Ghebreyesus, ya ce har yanzu ba a bar dukkan ƙasashe su canza yanayin cutar ba.
Idan ƙasashe za su iya tantance, bincika, warkar, ware, kuma su bi mutane da su, za su iya ba da amsa.
Muna cikin damuwa sosai game da yawan masu cutar da kuma rashin kulawarsu.
A cewar Dr. Tom Friedman, tsohon darektan Cibiyar Kula da Cututtuka da Cututtuka ta Amurka, cutar ta "ba ta da tabbas".
A wani rahoto da CNN ya fitar a watan Fabrairu, ya ce, "Baya ga mura, babu wata cutar da ke shiga cikin iska da aka gano tun daga lokacin da ta fara fitowa har zuwa yau da kullum".
Ghibrisus ya yi magana game da ra'ayi mai kama da juna, yana cewa "Ba mu taɓa ganin annobar da ke haifar da kwayar cutar ta corona ba".
Ya kara da cewa, "Kuma ba mu taba ganin wata annoba da za a iya sarrafawa a lokaci guda ba".
Sabuwar cutar ta zama annoba ta duniya bayan da WHO ta yanke shawarar a watan Janairu don ayyana gaggawar matsalar lafiyar jama'a mai matukar damuwa ta duniya.
Daraktan Cibiyar Kula da Cututtuka da Cututtuka ta Amurka, Dr. Anthony Fauci, ya ce game da barkewar cutar, "A takaice dai, yana kara ta'azzara".
A ranar Alhamis, Associated Press ta ba da rahoton cewa akwai aƙalla mutane 126,000 da suka kamu da cutar COVID-19 a duniya, wanda ya haifar da mutuwar sama da 4,600.
Cutar annobar coronavirus ta 2019-20 annoba ce mai ci gaba ta cutar coronavirus (COVID-19) wanda ke haifar da cututtukan cututtukan cututtukan cututtukan cututtukan cututtukan coronavirus 2 (SARS-CoV-2).
An gano barkewar cutar a Wuhan, China a watan Janairun 2019, an ayyana ta a matsayin gaggawa ta lafiyar jama'a ta kasa da kasa a ranar 30 ga Janairun 2020, kuma an ayyana ta a matsayin cutar ta duniya a ranar 11 ga Maris, 2020.
Ya zuwa 10 ga Afrilu 2020, an ba da rahoton kusan mutane miliyan 1.61 na COVID-19 a cikin ƙasashe da yankuna 210, wanda ya haifar da mutuwar kusan mutane 97,000.
Kimanin mutane 364,000 ne suka warke.
An kiyasta mutuwar ta kai kashi 4 cikin 100 a China, yayin da a duniya ta kai 13.04 bisa ɗari a Algeria da kuma kashi 0.08 cikin ɗari a New Zealand.
Alamun da ake yawan gani sun hada da tari, tari, da rashin numfashi.
Matsaloli na iya haɗawa da ciwon huhu da alamun cututtukan cututtukan cututtukan cututtukan numfashi.
Lokacin kamuwa da cutar zuwa lokacin bayyanar cututtuka shine kwanaki biyar, amma yana iya zama daga kwana biyu zuwa goma sha huɗu.
Babu wani maganin alurar riga kafi ko maganin rigakafi da aka sani.
Farkon magani shine bayyanar cututtuka da magani mai mahimmanci. Shawarwarin da aka ba da shawarar na farfadowa sun haɗa da wanke hannaye, rufe baki yayin da ake hauka, kiyaye nesa da wasu, da kuma sa ido da kuma keɓewa ga waɗanda ake zargin suna da cutar.
A duk duniya, hukumomi sun mayar da martani ta hanyar aiwatar da takunkumin tafiye-tafiye, keɓewa, takunkumin zirga-zirga, kula da haɗarin haɗari, da rufe wuraren.
Cutar ta haifar da rikicewar zamantakewar al'umma da tattalin arziki a duniya, jinkirta ko soke wasanni, addini, siyasa da al'adu, da kuma raguwar kayayyaki da aka yi amfani da su.
An rufe makarantu da jami'o'i a matakin ƙasa ko na gida a cikin ƙasashe 193, wanda ya shafi kusan kashi 99.4 na yawan ɗaliban ɗaliban duniya.
